<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Партнерская программа - Вакация</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bellota:wght@400;700&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css?v=<%= Date.now() %>">
    <style>
        .profile-layout { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr; 
            gap: 30px; 
            padding: 40px 0; 
            align-items: start;
        }
        .profile-sidebar { 
            background: #fff; 
            border-radius: 24px; 
            padding: 20px; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.04); 
            position: sticky;
            top: 100px;
        }
        .profile-menu { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
        .menu-btn { 
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            gap: 12px; 
            padding: 14px 20px; 
            border-radius: 16px; 
            border: none; 
            background: none; 
            color: #64748b; 
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; 
            font-weight: 600; 
            font-size: 15px; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); 
            text-align: left;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .menu-btn svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            stroke-width: 2px;
            transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }
        .menu-btn:hover { background: #f1f5f9; color: #1e293b; }
        .menu-btn:hover svg {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(5deg);
            color: #635bff;
        }
        .menu-btn.active { 
            background: #635bff; 
            color: #fff; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.25); 
        }
        .menu-btn.active svg {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            color: #fff;
        }
        .profile-content { 
            background: #fff; 
            border-radius: 24px; 
            padding: 40px; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.04); 
            min-height: 500px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .section-title { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #1e293b; }
        
        .vk-form-group { margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .vk-label { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .vk-input { 
            width: 100%; 
            padding: 16px 20px; 
            border-radius: 16px; 
            border: 2px solid #f1f5f9; 
            background: #f8fafc; 
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; 
            font-size: 15px; 
            font-weight: 600; 
            color: #1e293b; 
            transition: 0.3s; 
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .vk-input:focus { border-color: #635bff; background: #fff; outline: none; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.1); }
        
        .btn-submit-vk { 
            background: #635bff; 
            color: #fff; 
            padding: 18px 40px; 
            border-radius: 100px; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            border: none; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            transition: 0.3s; 
            width: 100%; 
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn-submit-vk:hover { background: #5249ff; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.2); }

        .status-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .status-icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .status-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .status-desc { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; }

        @media (max-width: 992px) { .profile-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .profile-sidebar { position: static; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="profile-layout">
            <aside class="profile-sidebar">
                <div class="profile-menu">
                    <a href="/organizer/dashboard" class="menu-btn">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"></line></svg>
                        Дашборд
                    </a>
                    <a href="/organizer/events" class="menu-btn">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
                        Мои мероприятия
                    </a>
                    <a href="/organizer/events/create" class="menu-btn">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg>
                        Создать мероприятие
                    </a>
                    <a href="/organizer/partner/apply" class="menu-btn active">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                        Партнерская программа
                    </a>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <main class="profile-content">
                <h1 class="section-title">Партнерская программа</h1>
                
                <% if (partner) { %>
                    <div class="status-card">
                        <div class="status-icon">
                            <%= partner.status === 'approved' ? '✅' : (partner.status === 'rejected' ? '❌' : '⏳') %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="status-title">
                            Статус заявки: 
                            <span style="color: <%= partner.status === 'approved' ? '#10b981' : (partner.status === 'rejected' ? '#ef4444' : '#635bff') %>">
                                <%= partner.status === 'approved' ? 'Одобрена' : (partner.status === 'rejected' ? 'Отклонена' : 'На рассмотрении') %>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="status-desc">
                            <% if (partner.status === 'approved') { %>
                                Поздравляем! Вы являетесь официальным партнером. Ваша ставка комиссии: <%= partner.commission_rate %>%
                            <% } else if (partner.status === 'rejected') { %>
                                К сожалению, ваша заявка была отклонена. Свяжитесь с поддержкой для уточнения причин.
                            <% } else { %>
                                Мы получили вашу заявку и свяжемся с вами в течение 24 часов.
                            <% } %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <form action="/organizer/partner/apply" method="POST">
                        <div class="vk-form-group">
                            <label class="vk-label">Название компании / ИП</label>
                            <input type="text" name="company_name" class="vk-input" required placeholder="ООО 'Событие'">
                        </div>
                        <div class="vk-form-group">
                            <label class="vk-label">ИНН</label>
                            <input type="text" name="inn" class="vk-input" required placeholder="10-значный номер">
                        </div>
                        <div class="vk-form-group">
                            <label class="vk-label">Контактная информация</label>
                            <textarea name="contact_info" class="vk-input" rows="4" required placeholder="Телефон, ссылка на сайт или соцсети..."></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-submit-vk">Отправить заявку</button>
                    </form>
                <% } %>
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
